data.text:
@zevlanderer @ari_eb 

I believe there are still several tests that need to be run before we can begin parsing as a mismatch between Yachin and the Mishna can indicate an error in the Mishna. Right now I'm writing a framework for the tests, once we get all the tags cleared up, I'll be able to run them.

Here's the link to the files. 
https://drive.google.com/drive/u/1/folders/0BwEntTcxGmMAeHBmTkJvbWFuSTQ

data.text:
Tests to run:
1) Check that MIshnayot are in order and increment by 1 - Steve
2) Check Perakim are in order in Yachin + Boaz.
3) Compare number of Yachin tags in Mishna with number of Yachin comments. Same for Boaz.
4) Make sure all files exist (or can be found). - Yoni
